comments.body:
@mheon i do get per-container stats on Arch with systemd, which seems correct (the expected result i mentioned is from real test running there).

On Alpine with OpenRC i get only the same sum values (i presume), shown with each container on stats list.

On Alpine i have `/sys/fs/cgroup/test/`, on Arch path is a lot more complicated, but it looks like there is a separate subpath per container, e.g., `/sys/fs/cgroup/.../user-libpod_pod_[pod SHA?].slice/libpod-[container-SHA?].scope/`
